title: Zombies, The - Greatest Hits Greatest Recordings
description:
[i]This is a 1995 mastering by Bob Fisher, Digital Domains. Not sure what equipment or masters were available but the levels seem to falls short of 22.5kHz. Look at this release as an archive of Transluxe 57803 more than anything else.

That aside, this has some amazing tracks such as She's Not There and Time of the Season which are haunting as much as historical.

Lastly, this CD has interview material with Rod Argent so please keep that in mind if making a playlist from the CDrip.

- Big Papi[/i]
